@Produces(segment="MRG", resource=org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Patient.class, extra={org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Account.class,org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Encounter.class}) public class MRGParser extends AbstractSegmentParser
Parser for MRG Segments The MRG segment populates a Patient resource with identifiers and demographics for a patient which would need to be merged into a single patiennt.
